top.value: GTMP grant from DFID used for mapping trachoma.

The goal of this project is to ensure that all occupational drivers have access to good quality refractive error and referral services for reduction of avoidable blindness and improvement in road safety
The aim of this project is to control and eliminate blinding trachoma as a public health problem.
